_sText:
Hello,
Made this in a few hours, about 5.
I'm kinda going through a thing, I seem to make lots of Dust "Themed" maps but I need ideas for some maps.
Please leave some feedback on ideas, of course you would be credited towards the final result.

The idea is that you;
Spawn>Run/Jump down to pit>Kill/Die>Respawn>Repeat.
Yea.
Plenty of props and decals.
This was a new idea, I dident see anything like this after a while of searching.
So I made my own, do leave feedback on makeing this better if you want.
This map features include;
Props from De_Dust & De_Dust2.
Junk/Rubbish props from De_Dust & De_Dust2
Lighting from De_Dust & De_Dust2.
3D Skybox from De_Dust2.
Decals from De_Dust & De_Dust2.
And much much more.

Hope you enjoy this map, if you could make ym day with a few seconds of your time, please assess this realisticly.
Thanks.


EJHF
